<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Christopher McGrath | Off-Market Real Estate Deals</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #111;
      background: #fff;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 48px 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-top: 64px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    p {
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .card {
      border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    ul {
      padding-left: 18px;
    }
    input, textarea, button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    button {
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 80px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">

    <h1>Christopher McGrath</h1>
    <p>
      Public off-market and flip-ready real estate contracts available for qualified cash buyers in Bergen County, New Jersey.
    </p>

    <h2>Available Contracts</h2>
    <p>All properties are under contract and offered via assignment of equitable interest.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <span class="badge">Available</span>
      <h3>123 Example St, Bergen County</h3>
      <p>Distressed single-family. Flip ready. Clear title.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>ARV: $750,000</li>
        <li>Estimated Rehab: $85,000</li>
        <li>Assignment Price: $525,000</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Submit an Offer</h2>
    <p>All offers are reviewed privately. Proof of funds required.</p>

    <form>
      <input placeholder="Full Name" />
      <input placeholder="Email Address" />
      <input placeholder="Phone Number" />
      <input placeholder="Property Address" />
      <input placeholder="Offer Amount ($)" />
      <input type="file" />
      <textarea rows="4" placeholder="Buyer experience / notes"></textarea>
      <button type="submit">Submit Offer</button>
    </form>

    <h2>Join Buyers List</h2>
    <p>Receive future off-market opportunities before public release.</p>

    <form>
      <input placeholder="Full Name" />
      <input placeholder="Email Address" />
      <input placeholder="Phone Number" />
      <textarea rows="4" placeholder="Buying criteria (budget, area, asset type)"></textarea>
      <button type="submit">Join Buyers List</button>
    </form>

    <footer>
      <p>© 2026 Christopher McGrath. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>Not a licensed real estate broker. Properties offered via equitable interest assignment only.</p>
      <p>For qualified real estate investors and cash buyers.</p>
    </footer>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
